These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  dressmaker, police-officer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, gospel
House: colonial, palace
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, blood-red
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the palace house##3
2. the police-officer is in an even position##4
3. the fan of gospel is the dressmaker##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Job      | dressmaker  | police-officer   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | funk   |
| House         | palace | colonial |
| Color     | red | blood-red    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: german, french
City: prague, liverpool
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, gardening
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, blood-red
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to prague is the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the french is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Nationality          | german     | french |
| City   | liverpool | prague  |
| Hobby           | gardening         | sudoku     |
| Color     | green   | blood-red    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, card-games
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, trance
There 2 different types of food: papaya, apricot
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, polish
1. the polish is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
2. the person eating apricot is on the right of the fan of trance##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Hobby    | card-games     | baking |
| Music-Genre         | trance | pop    |
| Food         | papaya         | apricot        |
| Nationality   | turkish         | polish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, musical
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, dressmaker
2 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, turquise
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the dressmaker is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person who likes turquise is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Movie-Genre      | musical     | drama |
| Job          | dressmaker   | security-guard  |
| Pet         | lizard | mouse     |
| Color   | coral  | turquise         |

