.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, fonseca
City: edinburgh, rome
House: cottage, colonial
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to rome is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fonseca-smoker is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the cottage house is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Cigar           | fonseca | ritmeester    |
| City   | edinburgh       | rome |
| House           | cottage         | colonial    |
| Birthday         | september    | october   |

