.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-11::.
House: cottage, colonial
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, camping
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, rose
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
2. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
3. the colonial house is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| House           | cottage | colonial |
| Beverage   | water    | iced-tea      |
| Hobby           | rock-climbing      | camping          |
| Flower         | rose | sunflower       |

