.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, sunflower
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, martial-arts
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, grey
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, trance
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
2. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
3. the fan of ambient is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Flower    | begonia | sunflower    |
| Movie-Genre         | martial-arts        | adventure |
| Color         | white          | grey     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient        | trance     |

 